cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper discusses the integration of Edge Computing and Artificial Intelligence, which falls under the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Software Engineering (cs.SE). The paper specifically talks about AI for edge and AI on edge, which are subtopics of Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of processing massive amounts of data generated at the network edge, which falls under Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing and Networking and Internet Architecture. Finally, the paper provides insights into the research roadmap for Edge Intelligence, which falls under Software Engineering.
